    "ExtraInfo": "Usage Scenario\n\nIn VLL or VPLS networking, to configure the granularity for Y.1731 statistics collection on the AC interface of a PW, run the y1731 measure-granularity command. You can specify either of the following parameters on the AC interface as needed:\n\nTo configure a port as the granularity for Y.1731 statistics collection, specify the port parameter. Statistics about all services on the port are collected.\nTo configure a port and all VLANs that the port joins as the granularity for Y.1731 statistics collection, specify the port-vlan parameter. Statistics about specified services on the port are collected.\n\n\nPrerequisites\n\nA MEP has been created using the mep mep-id command in the interface view."
